---
layout: default
---
.row-fluid
  .span12
    %h1 
      %i.icon-download-alt
      Download
    %p.lead Please feel free to choose a distribution most appropriate for you.
    .alert.alert-error
      %i.icon-info-sign
      %strong Please note
      That you can also join our
      %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/community"} Community
      and checkout the
      = succeed "." do
        %a{:href => "https://github.com/PerfCake/PerfCake"} source code repository
.row
  .span4
    %h3 
      %i.icon-gear
      Binary Distribution
    %p
      This a 
      %strong ready to run
      distribution of PerfCake. All you need is an installation of 
      %a{:href => "http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/"} Java SE 7
      or later.
    %p 
      This distribution format is not ready yet. Please check out later. We are sorry for the inconveniences. You could also try the source code download to the right, or the 
      = succeed "." do
        %a{:href => "https://github.com/PerfCake/PerfCake"} source code repository on GitHub
    %p
      %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-big.disabled{ :href=>'#download' } 
        %i.icon-download
        Download Binary Distribution &raquo; 
  .span4
    %h3 
      %i.icon-cogs
      Binary Distribution with Java SE installation
    %p
      This a 
      %strong ready to run
      distribution of PerfCake. You do not need any additional dependencies. We even included a Java SE installation for your comfort. The price for that is a slightly larger installation.
    %p 
      This distribution format is not ready yet. Please check out later. We are sorry for the inconveniences. You could also try the source code download to the right, or the 
      = succeed "." do
        %a{:href => "https://github.com/PerfCake/PerfCake"} source code repository on GitHub
    %p
      %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-big.disabled{ :href=>'#download' } 
        %i.icon-download
        Download Binary Distribution with JDK &raquo; 
  .span4
    %h3 
      %i.icon-keyboard
      Source Code Distribution
    %p
      This a distribution of the
      %strong master branch
      directly from our 
      = succeed "." do
        %a{:href => "https://github.com/PerfCake/PerfCake"} source code repository on GitHub
      This is recommended for advanced users.
    %p 
      You might be interested in how to 
      %a{ :href=>'#{site.base_url}/quickstart' } compile and run
      this distribution.
    %p
      %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-big{ :href=>'https://github.com/PerfCake/PerfCake/archive/master.zip' } 
        %i.icon-download
        Download Source Code Distribution &raquo; 
